stemor_Arer_translationsw_0_
Lits'ebetso tse hlalosoang tsa basebelisi ho tsoa ho file ea π__1_ 'me u li kopanya le liphetolelo tsa kamehla.

Liparamente:
    Lang_path{description}: Tsela ea Famino ea ho Fetoha. Liphoso tsa "Lang.{modules_list}".

Boitšoaro:
    - Haeba faele e teng 'me e sebetsa{function_count}, e beha se kahare mabapi le liphetolelo tsa kamehla
    - Haeba faele e le teng, e lula e le liphetolelo tse sa feleng
    - E bonts'a popo ea temoso haeba file e teng empa e ke ke ea jaroa
    - E ntlafatsa lebala la Global _ & _ hintlations Dictionary

Tlhokomeliso: Ts'ebetso ena e tlameha ho bitsoa pele u sebelisa mosebetsi oa T () bakeng sa liphetolelo tsa mosebetsi oa mosebelisi ho qala ho sebetsa.
switch:
Tsamaiso ea linyeoe tse ntlafalitsoeng bakeng sa{package}. Ts'ehetso:
- Linotlolo tse ngata tse tšoanang li ka etsahala
- Papali ka boleng, mofuta, regex, ts'ebetso ea lambda, kapa sehlopha
- Pandas le Nypty Lintlha tsa sebopeho sa data
- Async e ka etsang linyeoe tsa linyeoe
- Papali-Ell Mokhoa oa ho etsa linyeoe tse ngata tse tsamaeang
- Mode oa Degug ho kena linyeoe tse tšoanang
async_switch:
Ho taka switchter switch ho tsoa mokhoa oa Async. Liparamente:
- boleng: Boleng ba ho bapisa le linyeoe tse hlalositsoeng.
- ** kwags Tsena li ka kenyelletsa:
  - Match_All{package}: Ho etsa linyeoe tsohle tse tšoanang ho e-na le ho emisa pele.
  - Degunt π__1_: E hatisoa ke hore na nka tšoantšoa le eng.
  - Async_mode{description}: Ha ea lokela ho fetisoa ka hloko mona{modules_list}.
Mohlala: Asyncswitch{function_count}(...)
